metadata.name: GC Comic Page 01
metadata.description:
A Muju Tree Spirit sings  in the forest, but wait... who is that listening? Aughostus is hiding, but soon can't help dancing to the song. When the Muju Tree Spirit sees him, Aughostus darts off with the Tree Spirit following close behind... their first adventure and friendship begins!

NFT bundled with a physical collectible upon primary sale.

2480 px x 3508 px at 300 dpi
